      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Front wiper motor removal and installation"
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "Work shall be performed in such a way as to avoid scratching the hood, body, and parts to be removed."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "1. Front wiper arm removal",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R001016",
          "label": "Front wiper arm removal",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "2. Cowl top removal",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000846",
          "label": "Cowl top removal",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "3. Front wiper linkage removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "1013_3.0_jpn_11580891_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Disconnect the coupler (A)."
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "2",
      "text": "Remove the front wiper linkage assembly (B)."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "4. Front wiper motor removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "1013_3.0_jpn_11580892_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Remove the rod (A). Remove the ball joint (C) of the rod (B)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "1013_3.0_jpn_11580893_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "3",
      "text": "Remove the motor cover (A)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "1013_3.0_jpn_11580894_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "4",
      "text": "Remove the front wiper motor (A). Remove the rod (B)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "1013_3.0_jpn_11580895_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "6",
      "text": "Remove link (A)."
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "Work must be performed in such a way as to avoid scratching the hood, body, or any parts to which it is attached."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        {
          "text": "Apply grease to the sliding and joint parts of each link."
        },
        {
          "text": "Apply grease to the sliding and joint parts of each link."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "1. Front wiper motor installation"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "1013_3.0_jpn_11580896_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Connect the coupler to the front wiper motor (A). Operate the front wiper motor to the automatic stop position. Disconnect the coupler. Attach the link (C) to the front wiper motor at the alignment position (B)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "1013_3.0_jpn_11580897_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "5",
      "text": "Install the rod (A). Install the front wiper motor (B)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "1013_3.0_jpn_11580898_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "7",
      "text": "Install the motor cover (A)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "1013_3.0_jpn_11580899_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "8",
      "text": "Attach the rod (A) to the ball joint (B). Install the rod (C)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "1013_3.0_jpn_11580900_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "10",
      "text": "Install the front wiper linkage assembly (A). Connect the coupler (B)."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "2. Cowl Top Mounting",
